---

<section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 bg-gray-950 text-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-400"></span>
          ANCHR AI Labs
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
          The authority behind<br />Claude Cowork
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          ANCHR AI Labs is the company behind Claude Cowork. We design AI systems for businesses, run bootcamps for professionals, and deliver corporate training for teams making the shift from AI users to AI operators.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">
          {[
            '100+ global speaking engagements on AI, PR, and business systems',
            'PR + AI positioning expertise for founders and corporate teams',
            'AI systems consulting for businesses ready to scale beyond prompts',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-600/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-400 font-semibold hover:text-brand-300 transition-colors"
        >
          Learn more about ANCHR AI Labs →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-64 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-600/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-2xl">
          🧭
        </div>
        <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Founded in Singapore</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-5">
          Building at the intersection of AI systems, communications strategy, and operator training.
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">What we offer</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <li>→ AI Systems Bootcamp</li>
            <li>→ Corporate Training</li>
            <li>→ 1:1 Consulting</li>
            <li>→ Operator Certification</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
